{"_path":"/maps/_ai/operations/infrastructure","_dir":"operations","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"Infrastructure","description":"AI 基础设施与云平台，包括 Modal、Lambda Labs、SkyPilot 等 Serverless GPU 和多云编排方案。","original_path":"_ai/infrastructure.md","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"基础设施-infrastructure"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基础设施 (Infrastructure)"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"modalpython-原生的-serverless-gpu-平台"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Modal：Python 原生的 Serverless GPU 平台"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Modal 是面向 AI/ML 工程师的 Serverless 计算平台，核心卖点是\"Python-native\"——用纯 Python 代码定义计算任务，自动处理容器化、调度、扩缩容。支持从 0 到数百 GPU 的秒级扩容，按秒计费，用后即焚。内置高性能分布式文件系统，大模型权重秒级加载。适合快速原型验证和推理服务部署。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://modal.com/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Modal 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://modal.com/docs","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Modal 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://modal.com/blog/serverless-gpu-article","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Serverless GPU 对比"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"lambda-labs高性价比-ai-云服务商"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lambda Labs：高性价比 AI 云服务商"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lambda Labs 是专注 AI 工作负载的云服务商，以高性价比 GPU 实例著称。相比 AWS/GCP，Lambda 的 GPU 价格通常低 50%+，且提供即时可用的实例（无需排队）。支持 NVIDIA B200、H100、A100、GH200 等最新 GPU，提供按小时计费的 GPU 实例和长期租用的私有集群，是训练任务的性价比之选。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://lambda.ai/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lambda Labs 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://lambda.ai/pricing","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Lambda 定价"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://lambda.ai/blog/deepchat-3-step-training-at-scale-nvidia-h100-sxm5-vs-a100-sxm4","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"H100 vs A100 对比"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"skypilot多云-ai-编排框架"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SkyPilot：多云 AI 编排框架"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SkyPilot 是伯克利大学 Sky Computing Lab 开源的多云编排工具，目标是\"Run AI on Any Infrastructure\"。它抽象了不同云厂商的差异，支持 AWS、GCP、Azure、Lambda、Kubernetes、Slurm 等多种基础设施，自动选择最便宜的可用区域和实例类型，实例被抢占时自动迁移，让用户专注算法而非基础设施。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://skypilot.co/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SkyPilot 官网"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://docs.skypilot.co/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SkyPilot 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.usenix.org/system/files/nsdi23-yang-zongheng.pdf","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SkyPilot 论文"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"基础设施选型指南"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基础设施选型指南"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"快速原型和推理服务推荐 Modal，开发效率最高；长期训练任务推荐 Lambda Labs，性价比最优；多云和混合云场景推荐 SkyPilot，避免厂商锁定；企业级需求选择 AWS/GCP/Azure，生态最完善。实际选择应权衡开发效率、成本、可迁移性和合规要求。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://fullstackdeeplearning.com/cloud-gpus/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Cloud GPUs 完整对比"}]},{"type":"text","value":" | "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/skypilotvllmaws-vs-modal-which-platform-should-power-ai-ramkumar-zqghe","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SkyPilot vs Modal 对比"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"modalpython-原生的-serverless-gpu-平台","depth":2,"text":"Modal：Python 原生的 Serverless GPU 平台"},{"id":"lambda-labs高性价比-ai-云服务商","depth":2,"text":"Lambda Labs：高性价比 AI 云服务商"},{"id":"skypilot多云-ai-编排框架","depth":2,"text":"SkyPilot：多云 AI 编排框架"},{"id":"基础设施选型指南","depth":2,"text":"基础设施选型指南"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_ai:operations:infrastructure.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_ai/operations/infrastructure.md","_stem":"6.maps/_ai/operations/infrastructure","_extension":"md"}